    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices used to secure a metal cap-like plate with pins, which is typically marked with the identify of the vinyard or other information, over the bung of a wine barrel so that it is sealed and ready for transport. The device is usually spring-loaded.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
